SELENIUM-PRODUCT-BARCODE-NEG-001|Unknown barcode shows controlled empty state|/scanner|TYPE_AND_ASSERT_TEXT|css|input[name='barcode'],input[placeholder*='barcode'],input[placeholder*='Barcode'],input[type='search'],input[type='text']|0000000000000|Not found;No product;Unknown;Invalid;Barcode|P0|Validate unknown barcode does not produce broken or blank UI
